---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import whyImage from "@images/window-clean-wollongong-stadium.jpg";
---

<section>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Why our Window Cleaning Service</h2>
        <p>
            We’re not just another window cleaning business, we’re your local,
            reliable professionals who genuinely care about getting the job done
            right. Our attention to detail, friendly attitude, and commitment to
            showing up when we say we will sets us apart.
        </p>
        <Image
            src={whyImage}
            alt="Why our window service in wollongong"
            class="image"
        />
        <p>
            We take pride in delivering spotless windows, clear gutters, and
            cleaner homes and storefronts, without the hassle. Our mobile
            service means we come to you, on your schedule, with everything
            needed to make your windows shine.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    section {
        background-color: var(--light-blue);
    }
    .container {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 2rem;
    }
    .image {
        border-radius: 8px;
        width: 100%;
        height: auto;
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            grid-template-areas:
                "title title"
                "text-one text-one"
                " image text-two";
            gap: 3rem;
        }
        .container h2 {
            grid-area: title;
        }
        .container p:first-of-type {
            grid-area: text-one;
            width: 75%;
        }
        .container p:last-of-type {
            grid-area: text-two;
        }
        .image {
            grid-area: image;
        }
    }
    @media (min-width: 1024px) {
        .container {
            gap: 4rem;
        }
    }
</style>
